name: Statues 01 | Venus/Cupid
description:
Part of a collection for a study about narrative, composition, and light.
"for this statue, the idea is to show the pain on Venus's heart by leaving the Cupid alone in the forest, she needs to abandon him or the other Gods will kill Cupid because her seductive being look dangerous for the Gods"
You can see the full project, with some tests on Behance.net/animabob

Collection: STATUES (01 of 03)
